What I mean is that there exists prejudice in everyone. Of course bigotry is another matter.<br><br>
I may have appeared a bit heavyhanded as for my statement about Desert Storm. But, I have very strong feelings of the way American troops were misused during Vietnam. There was no attempt to contradict what you were saying.<br><br>
